headline: Could AES Acquisition Change EQT Corporation’s (EQT) Future Prospects?
summary: EQT Corporation (NYSE:EQT) is one of the 10 undervalued growth stocks for the next 5 years. According to a Bloomberg report released on February 3, BlackRock’s Global Infrastructure Partners (PIG) has joined forces with EQT Corporation (NYSE:EQT) in a potential bid to acquire power producer AES Corporation. headline: Alliant Energy to Post Q4 Earnings: What to Expect From the Stock?
summary: LNT gears up for Q4 results with storage expansion, data center demand and cost controls in focus, but earnings are seen declining year over year.
